Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.01,0:12:29.26,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b1\pos(630,678)}6.珠子与碗　　　高二 田山 和哉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.01,0:12:29.26,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b1\pos(630,773)}7.閉幕詞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.19,0:12:36.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才兩點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.19,0:12:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 這不是福部嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲 谷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你到了這裡 就說明你知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.41,0:12:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:53.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別裝傻了 當然是怪盜十文字了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:55.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:12:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那這就是下一場比試了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.21,0:13:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牆報部的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.96,0:13:02.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美工刀吧 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牆報部的傢伙們接招了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一號的頭條就是十文字的報道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且好像還打算用整份號外
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:13.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來報道捉到怪盜的團體
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.39,0:13:18.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過很抱歉 這次我贏定了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:20.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別看我這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.94,0:13:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我是推理迷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.94,0:13:25.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請手下留情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:27.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊原
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:30.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你讀過克里斯蒂的ABC謀殺案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:32.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那還用說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:34.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我想問你一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.25,0:13:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兇手按ABC的順序殺人有什麼理由嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會劇透的 沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:42.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:47.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為想按這個順序殺人 所以這麼做了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.18,0:13:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得會是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.06,0:13:53.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得這次事件的動機和ABC案同理？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.14,0:13:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五十音序的規律 久而久之大家都會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一點十文字應該也已經預料到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.48,0:14:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:10.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為這種盜竊方法應該還具有其他的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:13.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然 前提是犯人並非為取樂而偷盜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折木
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:19.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你莫非想抓住十文字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.88,0:14:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.13,0:14:22.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:24.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你很積極
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:26.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是既然千反田說她在意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.18,0:14:31.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那最後肯定是躲不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.18,0:14:33.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你無視她不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.93,0:14:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因為沒法無視她才麻煩的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:44.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.19,0:14:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 謝謝你的麵粉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:52.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.20,0:14:55.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你 居然要收錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說得那麼難聽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:15:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那袋麵粉是我以物易物換來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你給我樣東西來交換吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不就到此結束也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.05,0:15:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.42,0:15:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.22,0:15:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.93,0:15:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這合適嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 沒有這個你怎麼COS…痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.94,0:15:22.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說COSPLAY啊笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔術部 第5場公演即將開始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入須學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:46.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:48.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜歡魔術嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:53.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對魔術的瞭解倒是還沒有詳細到談得上喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.22,0:15:54.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…這很奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:58.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我只是有點意外
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:01.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:04.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:08.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}不過 也不用那麼說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是摩耶花的學姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.94,0:16:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天在漫研見過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.62,0:16:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你看那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦呀 田名邊學長和這位是…要敬禮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.21,0:16:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學生會長陸山宗芳閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲 女帝同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:27.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.47,0:16:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 福部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:32.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩位好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔術部公演現在開始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.85,0:16:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衷心感謝各位前來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬請欣賞我們魔術部全體成員
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.81,0:16:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每日不懈練習的技藝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.36,0:16:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:54.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這眾目睽睽之下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:56.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要如何偷東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:16:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪盜十文字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:17:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}那麼馬上就請高村洋一表演「活死人」…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:07.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:11.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 蠟燭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:11.84,50,NTP,110,0,0,,き{\c&HFFFFFF&}ゃんどる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.59,0:17:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.93,0:17:20.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:23.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了表演人員之外根本沒人靠近過舞台啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一開始就已經被偷走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:33.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是為什麼在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔細想想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.74,0:17:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本沒有證據表明十文字會在公演時偷東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.79,0:17:48.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像比昨天賣得多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.67,0:17:49.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是賣得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.17,0:17:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許是因為海報起了作用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:52.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:58.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然應該按學姐說的做嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:01.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不是嘛 要不是某人莫名其妙的反對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.47,0:18:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天也能賣得更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:06.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了算了 這麼說人家豈不是太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.19,0:18:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.65,0:18:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.11,0:18:12.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到底 什麼沒找到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:13.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就是在說謊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:18.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實是突然不敢把不怎麼樣的漫畫拿來見人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.82,0:18:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說出那種聽都沒聽過的同人本
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想充內行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:28.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正根本不可能有那種漫畫嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.25,0:18:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:30.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住口 到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然沒聽過那就閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.76,0:18:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可 可是 學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:39.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們沒聽到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.26,0:18:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不知道那就閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.89,0:18:49.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 部長 魔術部怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 看得很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.11,0:18:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 明天我也去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.61,0:18:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:18:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表演是什麼時候開始？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:19:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一天會表演好幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:02.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得應該沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.87,0:19:05.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 我出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:23.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真丟人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然想逃到阿福他們那裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊原
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.65,0:19:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…我在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:39.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湯淺學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.32,0:19:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起呢 事態變得這麼尷尬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:46.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學姐你沒有必要道歉呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我一直沒有開口 雖然想幫你說幾句話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:53.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.54,0:19:56.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會演變成河內學姐和湯淺學姐的對立了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:19:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不希望變成那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.30,0:20:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.05,0:20:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞也子她不是真心的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞也子？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.05,0:20:06.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是河內
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她叫河內亞也子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼知道她不是真心的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:17.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為亞也子和我是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.98,0:20:18.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就憑這個理由？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:22.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞也子和春菜也是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.61,0:20:24.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春菜？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.49,0:20:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安城春菜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「傍晚便成骸」的作者之一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.50,0:20:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是合作本嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:36.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作畫是另一個人負責的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.17,0:20:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞也子可能知道那個人是誰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:41.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人是幾年幾班的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.34,0:20:44.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…春菜已經不在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她轉學了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:48.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.52,0:20:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 就憑河內學姐和那位安城春菜是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼就能說她不是真心的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.27,0:21:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.94,0:21:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 我也無法再多解釋什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.95,0:21:07.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為 亞也子是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.45,0:21:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為一解釋就會變成在說河內學姐的壞話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.37,0:21:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再冷靜一會兒就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:19.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊原
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:22.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很快…就會回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.22,0:21:31.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,號外號外
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.77,0:21:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可錯過哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.81,0:21:40.15,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz270\fn@FZLiBian-S02\fs60\b1\pos(1564,254)}暗中活躍的怪盜十文字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.81,0:21:40.15,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz270\fn@FZLiBian-S02\fs60\b1\pos(699,254)}下一個目標將會是誰?!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,==========以下報道內容，時間軸請自行把握=========
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.15,0:21:43.15,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&H223836&}…是這麼回事。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.15,0:21:44.65,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&H223836&}而且，且看這位無禮之徒竟犯下何等豈有此理之事！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.65,0:21:47.07,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&H223836&}此人竟自我牆報部盜走美工刀。這毫無疑問是對媒體的公然挑釁。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.07,0:21:47.82,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&H223836&}阻止十文字盜竊行為的良策…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.91,0:21:49.95,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&H223836&}以上就是我方目前所掌握的情報。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.95,0:21:52.70,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&H223836&}因此，各位讀者，我們推測『十文字』最後的惡行將會發生在第三日中午十二點到下午二點之間，
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.70,0:21:53.41,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&H223836&}目標可能是『古典部』或『製作部』。
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,====================報道內容完畢===================
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.04,0:21:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠垣內學長…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.59,0:22:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被擺了一道啊 奉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.84,0:22:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔術部的蠟燭被偷走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.51,0:22:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犯罪聲明也找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.93,0:22:12.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.47,0:22:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望十文字別在摸到古典部來之前被捉住
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.10,0:22:18.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛 話是這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.40,0:22:21.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為能當場抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.73,0:22:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得他會在公演時偷東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.32,0:22:24.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.40,0:22:28.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十文字根本沒定下犯案時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.49,0:22:31.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,料理研的圓勺也是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.29,0:22:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是注意到了就告訴我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.75,0:22:38.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又不知道你打算抓現行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.83,0:22:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛 倒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.63,0:22:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.71,0:22:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入須學姐那裡寄賣的20本「冰菓」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.59,0:22:50.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說銷路不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.93,0:22:53.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛 畢竟是那個入須的手腕嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.10,0:22:55.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.56,0:23:00.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牆報部下午四點的號外報道了十文字事件
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.48,0:23:03.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還寫出了五十音序的規律
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.98,0:23:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典部的名字也登出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.24,0:23:09.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是十文字最後的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.36,0:23:11.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能會是古典部或者製作部
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.95,0:23:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,製作部…還有這種社團嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:15.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來的確是有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.37,0:23:18.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是去了那邊我們的算盤就落空了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.75,0:23:22.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天我想去找廣播部談談
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.17,0:23:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是校內廣播能採訪古典部的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.72,0:23:29.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.92,0:23:33.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我說你不累嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.30,0:23:33.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.80,0:23:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 摩耶花
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.51,0:23:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天賣得怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.64,0:23:40.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除去交給入須寄賣的20本 一共賣了16本
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.73,0:23:42.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經很可喜了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.27,0:23:45.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可喜…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.73,0:23:47.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.74,0:23:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1102.5,676.5)\fnFZLiBian-S02\fs82.5\b1\c&H070707&\3c&HE6E6E6&\frz24.07}剩餘137本
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.58,0:24:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到處託人幫忙雖然是我份內的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.92,0:24:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是總覺得好累…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.10,0:24:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「Body Talk」…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.35,0:24:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然比「傍晚便成骸」遜色一些
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.06,0:24:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這本也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.03,0:24:35.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我畫的要遜色百倍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.58,0:24:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奉太郎變了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.49,0:24:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 他開始發揮自己真正的價值了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.54,0:24:44.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以與千反田同學的邂逅為契機
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.04,0:24:48.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他成為了我無比欣賞的 充滿著意外的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.92,0:24:51.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我究竟
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.92,0:24:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是對此感到喜聞樂見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.60,0:24:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嫌疑人有一千多個
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.68,0:25:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通過推理從中揪出犯人這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.43,0:25:03.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任誰都不可能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.15,0:25:06.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼能採取的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.73,0:25:08.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就只有當場逮住這一個辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.82,0:25:12.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奉太郎沒有用武之地的這起事件的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.65,0:25:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就由我來揭開
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.45,0:25:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.28,0:25:20.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會抓住十文字的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.96,0:25:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 原來還能郵購嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.50,0:25:33.51,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3\fs48\pos(722,890)}歡迎來到KANYA祭！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.23,0:27:09.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 最後的目標
